title: Metallica - [Through The Never 2013] Feature Movie 1hr 32min
description:
www.imdb.com/title/tt2172935/

As the rock band Metallica performs a roaring set for fans in a sold-out arena, a young roadie named Trip [Dane DeHaan] is sent on a mission to meet a disabled truck and retrieve a particular item. 

However, the routine task turns into a surreal odyssey when Trip's van is hit by another vehicle and he finds himself up against a death dealing horseman. 

As Trip flees through desolate streets, he has only his wits to help him avoid the deadly equestrian and deliver Metallica's cargo.
